Package org.aavso.tools.vstar.ui.dialog

Class Summary
AboutBox This class creates and displays VStar's About Box.
AbstractOkCancelDialog This abstract class should be subclassed by any class that wants to have modal OK-Cancel dialog behaviour.
AbstractPlotControlDialog A dialog that controls the features of plots.
DiscrepantReportDialog This dialog is used to display information about a star that has been marked as discrepant in order to optionally add commentsField and submit to AAVSO.
FileExtensionFilter File extension based file filter for file dialog.
HelpContentsDialog This class represents a help content frame.
InfoDialog Information dialog for the currently loaded document.
LoginDialog This class encapsulates the behaviour of a generic modal login dialog box.
MessageBox Message dialog box utility class.
ObservationDetailsDialog This modeless dialog class displays info about a single observation.
PeriodAnalysisParameterDialog This modal dialog class allows period analysis parameters to be entered.
PhaseParameterDialog This class represents a dialog to obtain parameters for phase plot calculation: period, epoch.
PhasePlotControlDialog The phase plot control dialog.
PolynomialDegreeDialog This dialog allows the user to select the polynomial degree to be used for a polynomial fit operation.
RawPlotControlDialog The raw plot control dialog.
StarGroupSelectionPane This class represents a widget that permits a star group to be selected from a pop-up list and a star in that group from another pop-up list.
StarSelectorDialog This dialog allows the user to select a star.
